class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104iqs1665702628884.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iqs1665702628884.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iqs1665702628884.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"iqs1665702628884\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether the widget is displayed within square brackets; it is applicable only in character mode. Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Yes</code> (default), <code class=\"ph codeph\">No</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Fit</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iqs1665702628884__section_w799ab1b5b1_w800ab1b5_w801ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"iqs1665702628884__table_d12128e1_d12129e1_d12130e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iqs1665702628884__table_d12128e1_d12129e1_d12130e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iqs1665702628884__table_d12128e1_d12129e1_d12130e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqs1665702628884__table_d12128e1_d12129e1_d12130e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Yes</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqs1665702628884__table_d12128e1_d12129e1_d12130e1__entry__2\">The value of the field is displayed between\n                        square brackets if it is at least three characters wide, for example,\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">[OK]</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqs1665702628884__table_d12128e1_d12129e1_d12130e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">No</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqs1665702628884__table_d12128e1_d12129e1_d12130e1__entry__2\">No decoration is applied.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqs1665702628884__table_d12128e1_d12129e1_d12130e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Fit</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqs1665702628884__table_d12128e1_d12129e1_d12130e1__entry__2\">If there is space on the form, the field is\n                        displayed between square brackets. If not, one or both of the brackets are\n                        not displayed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iqs1665702628884__section_rjx_v4h_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d251386e124\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"iqs1665702628884__ul_yss_2q4_cxb\">\n<li class=\"li\">ucheckbox (CheckBox)</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Command button</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fxi1688449052174.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ucheckbox (CheckBox)</a><p>The ucheckbox widget enables the user to set a Boolean value in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called CheckBox, which is mapped to ucheckbox.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>CommandButton</a><p>The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613766\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613766\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Decoration Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 This property determines whether the widget is displayed within square brackets; it is applicable only in character mode. Valid values are Yes (default), No , or Fit . Value Description Yes The value of the field is displayed between square brackets if it is at least three characters wide, for example, [OK] . No No decoration is applied. Fit If there is space on the form, the field is displayed between square brackets. If not, one or both of the brackets are not displayed. Applies To ucheckbox (CheckBox) Command button Related Links ucheckbox (CheckBox) The ucheckbox widget enables the user to set a Boolean value in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called CheckBox, which is mapped to ucheckbox. CommandButton The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}